Thrain Ironhand is a character {
    species dwarf
    occupation smith
    status alive
    traits [meticulous, gruff, dependable]
    member of the Silver Compact
    located at Dawnwatch Keep
    allied with Kael Stormborn

    """
    Master artificer of Dawnwatch Keep and the finest weaponsmith
    in the Iron Kingdoms. He forged the Blade of First Light and
    maintains the Order's arsenal. His left hand is a mechanical
    prosthetic of his own design.
    """

    dialogue "greeting" {
        text "The dwarf glances up from his forge, sparks dancing off his mechanical hand. What do you need?"

        choice "I need a weapon" {
            response "He grunts approvingly. I can forge you something, but good steel takes time and coin. Come back when you're ready."
        }

        choice "Tell me about the Blade of First Light" {
            response "His eyes gleam with pride. My finest work. Forged from ore pulled from the Sundering crater itself. It burns undead on contact."
            effect "set knowledge.blade_of_first_light true"
        }

        choice "Kael sent me" {
            when "player has quest.join_order"
            response "Ah, so you want to join the Order? Then you'll need proper arms. Let me see what I can fit you with."
            effect "set quest.armed true"
        }
    }
}

